{"article_id":"kIJhXzC5r1wQqUsr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Snowden said","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"he misses a lot of things about his life in the United States .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Snowden :","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"It was worth it","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"NEW YORK -","depth":2},{"id":5,"text":"NSA leaker Edward Snowden on Saturday defended his disclosure of reams of classified information","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"his actions were worth fleeing his seemingly idyllic life in Hawaii and ending up in hiding in Russia ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"where he was joined by his girlfriend in July .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"\" It was about getting the information back to people","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"so they could decide","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"if they cared about it ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and on that account ... I could not have been more wrong","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"in thinking","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"that people wouldn ' t care , \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"he told a New Yorker Festival audience Saturday afternoon via webcast from an undisclosed location in Moscow .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"But he also suggested","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"if he had been a journalist","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"handling the leaked documents ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"he would have been more conservative than some of the reporters","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"who wrote about the surveillance programs .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Snowden said","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"he was just \" one small guy , \" an \" ordinary \" man","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"who saw the inner belly of the U.S. intelligence apparatus","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and had to act .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"He has been criticized by many inside and outside government","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"who have charged","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that he ' s a traitor","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"who jeopardized critical national security programs","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and made it easier for terrorists to plot and evade U.S. government surveillance .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"But Snowden has been hailed as a hero by civil liberties groups and libertarians","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"for revealing the extent of government surveillance into the communications of ordinary Americans .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Snowden implied","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"he had been vindicated by President Barack Obama ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"who said in January","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that a debate on surveillance \" will make us stronger \" as a country .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Obama ' s statement was \" very important for everybody","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"who believes","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that our rights matter ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"our constitution matters","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and intelligence agencies ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"even if they have good intentions ,","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"can go too far ,","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"when they violate the constitution on a massive scale ,","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"that matters ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and they need to be held to account for it , \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he said to questions by New Yorker staff writer Jane Mayer .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Snowden ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who worked with the journalists Glenn Greenwald , Laura Poitras , and Bart Gellman","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to bring highly classified materials about NSA surveillance programs to the public eye ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"also responded to a Mayer question","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that he summarized","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"by saying ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"\" Do I agree with all of the stories","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that the journalists have presented ? \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"\" I don ' t , \"","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he went on .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" I would draw those lines a little differently ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and I think much more conservatively","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"than some of the journalists have , \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"without naming which reporters ' stories he disagreed with .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Snowden also said","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"that \" in fact we ' ve seen serial violations of the law ...","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"NSA employees have used this surveillance power","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"to spy on exes ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"to spy on lovers ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"and that ' s a felony ;","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"however , none of them were prosecuted","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"because it was considered that the value of the programs was greater than the interests of justice . \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Mayer , the event ' s moderator , also delved into more personal questions","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"and asked Snowden","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"what he missed about the U.S. , a country","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"he may never return to .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"\" The question is , what don ' t I miss ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"whether it ' s my family ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"whether it ' s my home ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"whether it ' s my friends ,","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"whether it ' s my work at the agency ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"I was fulfilled and happy , \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"he responded .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"\" Things as simple","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"as having my old beat-up car ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"there ' s a lot","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to miss .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"It ' s a great country . \"","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Now , he ' s ensconced in Moscow ,","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"where he has reunited with his girlfriend Lindsay Mills ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"as revealed in a new documentary , \" Citizenfour , \" and a New Yorker piece","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"published on Friday .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" She was not entirely pleased","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"[ with what happened ] ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"but at the same time , it was an incredible reunion","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"because she understood me ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"and that meant a lot to me , \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"he said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":191,"left":99,"right":190,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":4,"right":189,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":141,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":119,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":102,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":5,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":6,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":114,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":108,"right":113,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":104,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":9,"right":103,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":12,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"l